"{\n    \"Title\": \"Notes to the Financial Statements15. Consumer Advancement Fund\",\n    \"row 1\": \"The Consumer Advancement Fund is established pursuant to Section 139(1) of the\",\n    \"row 2\": \"Business Practices and Consumer Protection Act (\\u201cAct\\u201d) and is funded by proceeds from\",\n    \"row 3\": \"court ordered actions taken against violators of the Act and various administrative\",\n    \"row 4\": \"penalties. It is created to fund education of consumers and suppliers on compliance with\",\n    \"row 5\": \"the Act. These funds are maintained in trust and administered by and do not form part of\",\n    \"row 6\": \"the assets of Consumer Protection BC. The statement of financial position and\",\n    \"row 7\": \"statement of operations and fund balance of the Consumer Advancement Fund at\",\n    \"row 8\": \"December 31, 2017 are as follows:\",\n    \"row 9\": \"Statement of Financial Position 2017 2016\",\n    \"row 10\": \"Cash $ 299,470 $ 350,240\",\n    \"row 11\": \"Due from Consumer Protection BC 28,747 500\",\n    \"row 12\": \"Total assets $ 328,217 $ 350,740\",\n    \"row 13\": \"Fund balance $ 328,217 \\u00a7 350,740\",\n    \"row 14\": \"Total fund balance $ 328,217 \\u00a7$ 350,740\",\n    \"row 15\": \"Statement of Operations 2017 2016\",\n    \"row 16\": \"Revenue $ 55,494 $ 14,204\",\n    \"row 17\": \"Interest 3,562 3,744\",\n    \"row 18\": \"59,056 17,948\",\n    \"row 19\": \"Expenses 81,579 85,199\",\n    \"row 20\": \"Deficiency of revenue over expenses (22,523) (67,251)\",\n    \"row 21\": \"Fund balance, beginning of year 350,740 417,991\",\n    \"row 22\": \"Fund balance, end of year $ 328,217 $ 350,740\",\n    \"row 23\": \"16. Recoveries Fund\",\n    \"row 24\": \"Recoveries consist of cost recoveries from legal actions and settlements Consumer\",\n    \"row 25\": \"Protection BC managed on behalf of consumers. Pursuant to a court order or consent\",\n    \"row 26\": \"agreement, Consumer Protection BC is authorized to deduct the costs it has incurred\",\n    \"row 27\": \"from the gross settlement proceeds prior to distributing the net amount to the damaged\",\n    \"row 28\": \"parties. Settlement amounts will vary from year to year depending upon the results of the\",\n    \"row 29\": \"actions taken. The statement of financial position and statement of operations and fund\",\n    \"row 30\": \"balance of the Recoveries Fund at December 31, 2017 are as follows:\"\n}"